text: Thousand Oaks is a city in southeastern Ventura County, California. It is part of the Greater Los Angeles Area in the United States. The city is located about from Los Angeles County, and to Downtown Los Angeles. It was named after the many oak trees that grew in the area. The city seal has a picture of an oak tree.
